# Registration System

## Dynamic Registration Forms

Administrator can create forms without coding.

Supported field types:

* Text
* Email
* Phone
* Number
* Date
* Select
* Radio
* Checkbox
* Text Area
* File Upload

---

## Conditional Logic

Example:

If applicant selects "University Student"

Show:

* University
* Faculty
* Year

If applicant selects "School Student"

Show:

* School
* Grade

